            "text": "[![LegislationCrest](/images/crests/ukpga.gif)](/ukpga/2009/6/introduction/enacted?view=plain)",
            "tokenCum": 43,
            "children": [
                {
                    "type": "Heading",
                    "prefix": "#",
                    "text": "Geneva Conventions and United Nations Personnel (Protocols) Act 2009",
                    "tokenCum": 63,
                    "wordSum": 9,
                    "tokenSum": 21,
                    "tokenCount": 20
                },
                {
                    "type": "Heading",
                    "prefix": "#",
                    "text": "2009 CHAPTER 6",
                    "tokenCum": 71,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "Text",
                            "prefix": "",
                            "text": "An Act to amend the Geneva Conventions Act 1957 so as to give effect to theProtocol additional to the Geneva Conventions of 12 August 1949 done on 8December 2005; and to amend the United Nations Personnel Act 1997 so as togive effect to the Optional Protocol to the Convention on the Safety of UnitedNations and Associated Personnel adopted by the General Assembly of the UnitedNations on 8 December 2005.",
                            "tokenCum": 187,
                            "wordSum": 69,
                            "tokenSum": 117,
                            "tokenCount": 117
                        }
                    ],
                    "wordSum": 72,
                    "tokenSum": 126,
                    "tokenCount": 8
                },
                {
                    "type": "Text",
                    "prefix": "",
                    "text": "[2nd July 2009]",
                    "tokenCum": 197,
                    "wordSum": 3,
                    "tokenSum": 11,
                    "tokenCount": 10
                },
                {
                    "type": "Text",
                    "prefix": "",
                    "text": "Be it enacted by the Queen\u2019s most Excellent Majesty, by and with the adviceand consent of the Lords Spiritual and Temporal, and Commons, in this presentParliament assembled, and by the authority of the same, as follows:\u2014",
                    "tokenCum": 254,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "Heading",
                            "prefix": "## 1",
                            "text": "Amendments of the Geneva Conventions Act 1957",
                            "tokenCum": 270,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(1)",
                                    "text": "The Geneva Conventions Act [1957 (c. 52)](/id/ukpga/1957/52?view=plain \"Goto item of legislation\") is amended as follows.",
                                    "tokenCum": 321,
                                    "wordSum": 15,
                                    "tokenSum": 53,
                                    "tokenCount": 53
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(2)",
                                    "text": "In section 1 (grave breaches of Conventions and protocols), in subsection(1), for \u201cor the first protocol\u201d substitute \u201c, the first protocol or the thirdprotocol\u201d.",
                                    "tokenCum": 362,
                                    "wordSum": 24,
                                    "tokenSum": 43,
                                    "tokenCount": 43
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(3)",
                                    "text": "In subsection (1A) of that section, after paragraph (b) insert \u201c; and",
                                    "tokenCum": 382,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(c)",
                                            "text": "a grave breach of the third protocol is anything which for the purposes ofArticle 6 of the protocol constitutes the perfidious use of the emblemspecified in section 6(1)(f) of this Act\u201d.",
                                            "tokenCum": 430,
                                            "wordSum": 31,
                                            "tokenSum": 51,
                                            "tokenCount": 51
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 43,
                                    "tokenSum": 73,
                                    "tokenCount": 21
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(4)",
                                    "text": "In section 6 (use of the Red Cross and other emblems), in subsection (1),after paragraph (e) insert \u201c;",
                                    "tokenCum": 460,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(f)",
                                            "text": "the emblem of a red frame in the shape of a square on edge on a whiteground, conforming to the illustration in Article 1 of the Annex to the thirdprotocol (and whether or not incorporating another emblem, or a combination ofemblems, in accordance with Article 3 of the protocol), or the designation\u201cRed Crystal\u201d or \u201cthird Protocol emblem\u201d\u201d.",
                                            "tokenCum": 547,
                                            "wordSum": 57,
                                            "tokenSum": 90,
                                            "tokenCount": 90
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 75,
                                    "tokenSum": 122,
                                    "tokenCount": 31
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(5)",
                                    "text": "After subsection (4A) of that section, insert\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 560,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Text",
                                            "prefix": "",
                                            "text": "\u201c(4B)Subsection (4) of this section shall apply in relation to a design orwording reproducing or resembling the emblem or a designation specified inparagraph (f) of subsection (1) of this section as it applies to designs orwording reproducing or resembling an emblem or designation specified inparagraph (b) or (c) of that subsection.",
                                            "tokenCum": 646,
                                            "wordSum": 51,
                                            "tokenSum": 89,
                                            "tokenCount": 89
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 58,
                                    "tokenSum": 104,
                                    "tokenCount": 14
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "(4C)But subsection (4) of this section shall not apply by virtue of subsection(4B) of this section where the use of the design or wording concerned is suchas would appear, in time of armed conflict, to confer the protection of thescheduled conventions and, where applicable, the first protocol and the secondprotocol.",
                                    "tokenCum": 719,
                                    "wordSum": 50,
                                    "tokenSum": 75,
                                    "tokenCount": 75
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "(4D)For the purposes of subsection (4B) of this section references insubsection (4) of this section to the passing of this Act shall be construedas references to the passing of the Geneva Conventions and United NationsPersonnel (Protocols) Act 2009.\u201d",
                                    "tokenCum": 783,
                                    "wordSum": 38,
                                    "tokenSum": 66,
                                    "tokenCount": 66
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(6)",
                                    "text": "In section 6A (regulations), in subsection (1)(b), for \u201cor the secondprotocol\u201d substitute \u201c, the second protocol or the third protocol\u201d.",
                                    "tokenCum": 818,
                                    "wordSum": 20,
                                    "tokenSum": 37,
                                    "tokenCount": 37
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(7)",
                                    "text": "In section 7 (interpretation), at the end of subsection (1) add \u201c;",
                                    "tokenCum": 839,
                                    "wordSum": 12,
                                    "tokenSum": 23,
                                    "tokenCount": 23
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "\u201cthe third protocol\u201d means the Protocol, additional to the Geneva Conventionsof 12 August 1949, relating to the Adoption of an Additional DistinctiveEmblem (Protocol III) done on 8 December 2005, the text of which is set out inSchedule 7\u201d.",
                                    "tokenCum": 911,
                                    "wordSum": 38,
                                    "tokenSum": 74,
                                    "tokenCount": 74
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(8)",
                                    "text": "After Schedule 6 (which sets out the text of the second protocol), insertthe Schedule 7 contained in the Schedule to this Act (which sets out the textof the third protocol).",
                                    "tokenCum": 953,
                                    "wordSum": 30,
                                    "tokenSum": 44,
                                    "tokenCount": 44
                                }
                            ],
                            "wordSum": 410,
                            "tokenSum": 731,
                            "tokenCount": 16
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "Heading",
                            "prefix": "## 2",
                            "text": "Amendments of the United Nations Personnel Act 1997",
                            "tokenCum": 968,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(1)",
                                    "text": "Section 4 of the United Nations Personnel Act [1997 (c.13)](/id/ukpga/1997/13?view=plain \"Go to item of legislation\") (meaning of \u201cUNworker\u201d) is amended as follows.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1030,
                                    "wordSum": 22,
                                    "tokenSum": 64,
                                    "tokenCount": 64
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(2)",
                                    "text": "In subsection (2)\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 1037,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(a)",
                                            "text": "for \u201csubsection (3)\u201d substitute \u201csubsections (3) and (3A)\u201d, and",
                                            "tokenCum": 1058,
                                            "wordSum": 9,
                                            "tokenSum": 24,
                                            "tokenCount": 24
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(b)",
                                            "text": "in paragraph (c)(i), for \u201cthe maintenance or restoration of internationalpeace and security\u201d substitute \u201ca purpose mentioned in subsection (2A)\u201d.",
                                            "tokenCum": 1092,
                                            "wordSum": 19,
                                            "tokenSum": 37,
                                            "tokenCount": 37
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 31,
                                    "tokenSum": 70,
                                    "tokenCount": 8
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(3)",
                                    "text": "After subsection (2) insert\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 1100,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Text",
                                            "prefix": "",
                                            "text": "\u201c(2A)The purposes referred to in subsection (2)(c)(i) are\u2014",
                                            "tokenCum": 1121,
                                            "wordSum": 8,
                                            "tokenSum": 24,
                                            "tokenCount": 24
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(a)",
                                            "text": "maintaining or restoring international peace and security;",
                                            "tokenCum": 1131,
                                            "wordSum": 7,
                                            "tokenSum": 13,
                                            "tokenCount": 13
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(b)",
                                            "text": "delivering humanitarian, political or development assistance inpeacebuilding;",
                                            "tokenCum": 1146,
                                            "wordSum": 7,
                                            "tokenSum": 18,
                                            "tokenCount": 18
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(c)",
                                            "text": "delivering emergency humanitarian assistance.\u201d",
                                            "tokenCum": 1155,
                                            "wordSum": 4,
                                            "tokenSum": 12,
                                            "tokenCount": 12
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 30,
                                    "tokenSum": 77,
                                    "tokenCount": 9
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(4)",
                                    "text": "After subsection (3) insert\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 1163,
                                    "wordSum": 4,
                                    "tokenSum": 10,
                                    "tokenCount": 10
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "\u201c(3A)In this section \u201cUN operation\u201d also does not include any operation inrespect of which a declaration is made in accordance with Article II(3) of theOptional Protocol (opt-out for operation to deliver emergency humanitarianassistance in response to natural disaster).\u201d",
                                    "tokenCum": 1227,
                                    "wordSum": 38,
                                    "tokenSum": 66,
                                    "tokenCount": 66
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(5)",
                                    "text": "In subsection (4), after the definition of \u201cthe Convention\u201d insert\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 1243,
                                    "wordSum": 10,
                                    "tokenSum": 18,
                                    "tokenCount": 18
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "\u201c\u201cthe Optional Protocol\u201d means the Optional Protocol to the Convention adoptedby the General Assembly of the United Nations on 8 December 2005;\u201d.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1278,
                                    "wordSum": 22,
                                    "tokenSum": 37,
                                    "tokenCount": 37
                                }
                            ],
                            "wordSum": 165,
                            "tokenSum": 358,
                            "tokenCount": 15
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "Heading",
                            "prefix": "## 3",
                            "text": "Commencement, extent and short title",
                            "tokenCum": 1286,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(1)",
                                    "text": "Sections 1 and 2 come into force on such day as the Secretary of State mayby order appoint.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1309,
                                    "wordSum": 18,
                                    "tokenSum": 25,
                                    "tokenCount": 25
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(2)",
                                    "text": "An order under subsection (1)\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 1318,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(a)",
                                            "text": "must be made by statutory instrument, and",
                                            "tokenCum": 1328,
                                            "wordSum": 7,
                                            "tokenSum": 13,
                                            "tokenCount": 13
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(b)",
                                            "text": "may make different provision for different purposes.",
                                            "tokenCum": 1336,
                                            "wordSum": 7,
                                            "tokenSum": 11,
                                            "tokenCount": 11
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 19,
                                    "tokenSum": 35,
                                    "tokenCount": 10
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(3)",
                                    "text": "Section 8(2) of the Geneva Conventions Act [1957 (c.52)](/id/ukpga/1957/52?view=plain \"Go to item of legislation\") (power toextend provisions to the Channel Islands, the Isle of Man and British overseasterritories) applies in relation to the provisions of section 1 and theSchedule as if they were contained in that Act.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1435,
                                    "wordSum": 47,
                                    "tokenSum": 101,
                                    "tokenCount": 101
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(4)",
                                    "text": "Section 9(2) of the United Nations Personnel Act [1997 (c.13)](/id/ukpga/1997/13?view=plain \"Go to item of legislation\") (power toextend provisions to the Channel Islands, the Isle of Man and British overseasterritories) applies in relation to the provisions of section 2 as if theywere contained in that Act.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1530,
                                    "wordSum": 45,
                                    "tokenSum": 97,
                                    "tokenCount": 97
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(5)",
                                    "text": "This Act may be cited as the Geneva Conventions and United NationsPersonnel (Protocols) Act 2009.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1559,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Text",
                                            "prefix": "",
                                            "text": "Section 1(8)",
                                            "tokenCum": 1565,
                                            "wordSum": 2,
                                            "tokenSum": 9,
                                            "tokenCount": 9
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 17,
                                    "tokenSum": 40,
                                    "tokenCount": 30
                                }
                            ],
                            "wordSum": 151,
                            "tokenSum": 307,
                            "tokenCount": 8
                        }
                    ],
                    "wordSum": 762,
                    "tokenSum": 1454,
                    "tokenCount": 57
                }
            ],
            "wordSum": 847,
